ma McDermott]], [[Falz]], [[Damilola Adegbite]], Uchemba Williams, [[Linda Osifo]] || Produced by A.Y || Feature Film\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of Nigerian film producers]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Inwang, Moses}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Nigerian filmmakers]]\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n", "name_user": "Nnadi Duke", "label": "safe", "comment": "Age adjustment under the profile picture by the right.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moses_Inwang"}
