{Wikiquote}}\n{{EB1911 poster|Turner, Joseph Mallord William}}\n* {{Cite Americana|short=1|wstitle=Turner, Joseph Mallord William|year=1920}}\n* {{Art UK bio}}\n* [http://www.turnersociety.org.uk/index.htm The Turner Society]\n* [http://www.christies.com/features/videos/gallery-talks/giudecca-la-donna-della-salute-san-giorgio.aspx Christie's Videos \u2013 ''Giudecca, La Donna della Salute'' and ''San Giorgio'' Joseph Mallord William Turner,RA]\n* [http://www.sothebys.com/video/privateview/N08516/index.html Sotheby's Videos \u2013 ''The Temple Of Jupiter Panellenius'' Joseph Mallord William Turner,RA]\n* [http://www.sothebys.com/video/privateview/L10033/index-turner.html Sotheby's Videos \u2013 ''Modern Rome Campo Vaccino'' and ''The condition of Modern Rome, Campo Vaccino'' J. M. W. Turner, RA]\n* [http://libmma.contentdm.oclc.org/cdm/search/field/contri/searchterm/Turner,%20J.%20M.%20W.%20(Joseph%20Mallord%20William),%201775-1851/mode/exact J.M.W. Turner exhibition catalogs]\n* [http://www.tate.org.uk/servlet/BrowseGroup?cgroupid=999999998 Web site of the Tate Turner Collection, includes the \"Turner Bequest\" of over 300 Oil paintings and over 30,000 sketches. The catalogue holds records of over 40,000 works by Turner]\n* {{Gutenberg author | id=Turner,+J.+M.+W.+(Joseph+Mallord+William)}}\n* {{Internet Archive author |sname=Joseph Mallord William Turner}}\n\n{{J. M. W. Turner|state=expanded}}\n{{Romanticism}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Turner, J. M. W.}}\n[[Category:J. M. W. Turner| ]]\n[[Category:1775 births]]\n[[Category:1851 deaths]]\n[[Category:18th-century English painters]]\n[[Category:19th-century English painters]]\n[[Category:British marine artists]]\n[[Category:British landscape painters]]\n[[Category:Burials at St Paul's Cathedral]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cholera]]\n[[Category:English landscape painters]]\n[[Category:English male painters]]\n[[Category:English printmakers]]\n[[Category:English romantic painters]]\n[[Category:English waterc